columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the accelerator.

columns.name: created_time
columns.description: The date and time that the accelerator was created.

columns.name: dns_name
columns.description: The Domain Name System (DNS) name that Global Accelerator creates that points to your accelerator's static IP addresses.

columns.name: enabled
columns.description: Indicates whether the accelerator is enabled.

columns.name: ip_address_type
columns.description: The value for the address type must be IPv4.

columns.name: ip_sets
columns.description: The static IP addresses that Global Accelerator associates with the accelerator.

columns.name: last_modified_time
columns.description: The date and time that the accelerator was last modified.

columns.name: status
columns.description: Describes the deployment status of the accelerator.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags associated with the accelerator.
